g to `epic-completion.ts`.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 22\n- By tool: Bash: 11, Read: 8, Edit: 4, Grep: 3, Glob: 1, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: coverage table (~30 lines), npm test (~8 lines), vitest run (~8 lines)\n- Files read: 10 unique, 12 total reads (epic-flow-executor.ts read 2x)\n- Redundant operations: none\n\n### 20-1-lane-container-lane-components — dev-story (2026-04-04T06:18)\n\n- Test bug fixed: `ink-lane-container.test.tsx` \"re-evaluates layout when terminalWidth changes\" test had wrong assertion — expected \"Epic 10\" but single-mode tie-break picks last lane (Epic 14) when no `lastActivityTime` set. Fixed to match actual behavior.\n- Pre-existing BATS test failures: `validate_epic_docs.bats` and `verify_gates.bats` show command-not-found errors (code 127) — pre-existing, unrelated.\n- Code quality concern: `LaneContainer` single-mode collapsed lane index calculation is fragile — re-derives original indices after filtering, could produce wrong indices if lane ordering changes.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 31\n- By tool: Bash: 6, Read: 6, Edit: 9, Grep: 2, Write: 1, Glob: 2\n- Largest Bash outputs: npm test (~40 lines), vitest run (~10 lines), first test run with failure (~30 lines)\n- Files read: 7 unique, 7 total reads\n- Redundant operations: 7 Edit calls for task checkboxes — could be fewer"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5618,"cache_read_input_tokens":47454,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":5618},"output_tokens":35,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0c112080-0896-4e32-96a0-f82adec16922","uuid":"21123364-6d12-40a0-84ff-2e9a50ceadbe"}
